==Greek==

===Noun===
'''ανατολή''' (anatolí) {{f}}

# [[east]]
# [[sunrise]], [[dawn]]
====Usage notes====
*"Aπό την ''ανατολή'' ως την δύση" thus means both "from east to west" and "from sunrise to sunset".

====Antonyms====
* [[δύση]]
